short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extention for tracking online judge practice status

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This app can help you record online judge practice status and take notes and summarize your practice history.

Hope it can improve your practice performance and get a great job!

Issues report: devapp915@gmail.com
